OL,3,CBeavers transform Dorset woodland into
OL,4,Cthriving wetland within a year
OL,6,FA pair of beavers have dramatically
OL,7,Freshaped their landscape a year after
OL,8,Ftheir release into the wild, turning a
OL,9,Fonce dense woodland into a rich and
OL,10,Fthriving wetland.
OL,12,FThe beavers are one of two pairs the
OL,13,FNational Trust released into Little
OL,14,FSea lake in Studland in Dorset, in
OL,15,FMarch 2025 under the first licence of
OL,16,Fits kind granted by Natural England.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
