OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774631480
OL,3,CBeavers transform Dorset woodland into
OL,4,Cthriving wetland within a year
OL,6,FTrail cameras have recently captured
OL,7,Ffootage of the beavers mating,
OL,8,Findicating there could be kits this
OL,9,Fsummer.
OL,11,FMs Crisford added: "It's very rare to
OL,12,Fcapture footage of beavers mating, so
OL,13,Fit has generated lots of interest.
OL,15,F"But the important thing for us was
OL,16,Fthat it's a clear sign they've settled
OL,17,Fwell into their new home.
OL,26,@sD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
