OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774631480
OL,3,CBeavers transform Dorset woodland into
OL,4,Cthriving wetland within a year
OL,6,F"Our monitoring programme, using
OL,7,Fdedicated volunteers and trail
OL,8,Fcameras, keeps us informed about the
OL,9,Fhealth and wellbeing of the beavers."
OL,11,FThe beavers joined another pair on the
OL,12,Flake which had arrived there by
OL,13,Funknown means prior to the Government
OL,14,Flicence being granted.
OL,16,FThat pair have successfully raised
OL,17,Fthree kits and constructed two large
OL,18,Flodges, one each side of the 33-
OL,19,Fhectare lake. Beavers' instinctive dam-
OL,20,Fbuilding plays an important role in
OL,21,Fclimate resilience.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
