PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774631480
OL,3,CBeavers transform Dorset woodland into
OL,4,Cthriving wetland within a year
OL,6,FBy slowing water flow and creating
OL,7,Fwetlands, beavers help retain water
OL,8,Fduring both floods and droughts,
OL,9,Fbenefiting nature and local
OL,10,Fcommunities.
OL,12,FTheir natural dams also filter out
OL,13,Fsediment, improving water quality
OL,14,Fdownstream.
OL,16,FThe next planned wild beaver release
OL,17,Fon the Purbeck Heaths National Nature
OL,18,FReserve is expected to take place this
OL,19,Fautumn, although the exact location
OL,20,Fhas yet to be confirmed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
